E1.notes:
* Both casts count as ability activations for the purposes of on-cast effects such as {{tip|Spellblade}} and stacking {{ai|Force Pulse|Kassadin}}.
* ''Jousting'' deals {{tip|area damage}} to all champions and large/epic monsters it hits, but {{tip|spell damage}} to all other struck targets.{{bug}}
** For this reason, ''Jousting'' kills {{cis|Yorick}} {{ai|Shepherd of Souls|Yorick|Mist Walkers}} and {{cis|Zyra}} grown plants in one hit.{{bug|2}}
* Casting {{ai|Chaaaaaaaarge!!!|Kled}} during ''Jousting'' will not interrupt the dash.
* Recasting ''Jousting'' while outside of maximum range will cause the ability to go on cooldown without activation.
* ''Jousting'' can be recast even while the target is {{tip|untargetable}}.
